1. Extra helper method is binary search to find the largest length of palindromic which is the consectutive characters are the same.
2. LongestPalindrome method is used to compare the same consecutive characters in two cases: 
   a. the number of same consecutive characters is odd.
   b. the number of same consecutive characters is even.
3. Choose the maximum one of the two case and choose the one as the final one. 
